i/2008/3157/regulation/4/3/b">4(3)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-a2fa63c9a473d5982368c906b80db07b" marker="F206"><p>Reg. 15(5)(ac) inserted (5.1.2009) by <ref eId="cm4g48vr3-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2008/3157">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) (No. 7) Regulations 2008 (S.I. 2008/3157)</ref>, <ref eId="cm4g48vr3-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2008/3157/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="cm4g48vr3-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2008/3157/regulation/4/3/c">4(3)(c)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-359d6d02907eaa2d696df74abdebefdf" marker="F207"><p>Reg. 15(5)(b) substituted (20.3.2017) by <ref eId="cq6huhy53-00008" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/174">The Social Security (Income-Related Benefits) Amendment Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/174)</ref>, <ref eId="cq6huhy53-00009" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/174/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="cq6huhy53-00010" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/174/regulation/4/2">4(2)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-1c439c9bb41d85a0a2dd5d114ee1d5da" marker="F208"><p>Words in reg. 15(5)(d) substituted (5.12.2005) by <ref eId="ch4uo0vo3-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2005/2877">The Civil Partnership (Pensions, Social Security and Child Support) (Consequential, etc. Provisions) Order 2005 (S.I. 2005/2877)</ref>, <ref eId="ch4uo0vo3-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2005/2877/article/1">art. 1</ref>, <ref eId="ch4uo0vo3-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2005/2877/schedule/3/paragraph/35/3">Sch. 3 para. 35(3)</ref> (with <ref eId="ch4uo0vo3-00010" class="subref" href="h