hedule/5/paragraph/94/b">Sch. 5 para. 94(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-784b0bea52a5ade5903a9b0c21e896cc" marker="F402"><p>Sch. II para. 13(7) inserted (with effect in accordance with regs.19 - 21 of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="cqaythge3-00016" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725">The Loans for Mortgage Interest Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/725)</ref>, <ref eId="cqaythge3-00017" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/regulation/1/2/a">reg. 1(2)(a)</ref>, <ref eId="cqaythge3-00018" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/schedule/5/paragraph/4/d/iii">Sch. 5 para. 4(d)(iii)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-0a7486c24c21868d7b9f11b2e5d12e39" marker="F403"><p>Sum in Sch. 2 para. 14(1)(a)  substituted (coming into force in accordance with art. 1(3)(k) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="ccx40v815-00008" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/242">The Social Security Benefits Up-rating Order 2024 (S.I. 2024/242)</ref>, <ref eId="ccx40v815-00009" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/242/article/1/3/k">arts. 1(3)(k)</ref>, <ref eId="ccx40v815-00010" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/242/article/29/4/a">29(4)(a)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-9ba03b128316ce521847c0bedd78f825" marker="F404"><p>Sum in Sch. 2 para. 14(1)(b)  substituted (coming into force in accordance with art. 1(3)(k) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="ccx40v815-00018" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/242">The Social Security Benefits Up-rating Order 2024 (S.I. 2024/242)</ref>, <ref eId="ccx40v815-00019" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/242/article/1/3/k">arts. 1(3)(k)</ref>, <ref eId="ccx40v815-00020" class="subref operative" href="http: