si/2018/676/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="cqc921bo3-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/676/regulation/2/4">2(4)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-1e559b13256e04d729a9c2b22132e0dd" marker="F462"><p>Words in <ref eId="co2l3x515-00006" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2002/1792/schedule/2A/paragraph/2/1">Sch. 2A para. 2(1)</ref> inserted (27.1.2025) by <ref eId="co2l3x515-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2025/3">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2025 (S.I. 2025/3)</ref>, <ref eId="co2l3x515-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2025/3/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="co2l3x515-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2025/3/regulation/2/2/a">2(2)(a)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-b795332f60da12bae9ddf018670fb8d4" marker="F463"><p>Word in <ref eId="co2lbdn85-00006" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2002/1792/schedule/2A/paragraph/4/3">Sch. 2A para. 4(3)</ref> omitted (27.1.2025) by virtue of <ref eId="co2lbdn85-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2025/3">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2025 (S.I. 2025/3)</ref>, <ref eId="co2lbdn85-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2025/3/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="co2lbdn85-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2025/3/regulation/2/2/b/i">2(2)(b)(i)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-ad5e2fed155d598db4ab4cc91c8a4eef" marker="F464"><p><ref eId="co2lbdn85-00015" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2002/1792/schedule/2A/paragraph/4/3/c">Sch. 2A para. 4(3)(c)</ref> and word inserted (27.1.2025) by <ref eId="co2lbdn8