/uksi/2013/630/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="cmyump3f3-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/630/regulation/33/7/b">33(7)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-539b8ed0961ee66e5fd7ef142dd24446" marker="F642"><p>Words in Sch. V Pt. I para. 20A(2)(j) substituted (29.10.2013) by <ref eId="cmzvd3z63-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/2536">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) (No. 3) Regulations 2013 (S.I. 2013/2536)</ref>, <ref eId="cmzvd3z63-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/2536/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="cmzvd3z63-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/2536/regulation/10/4">10(4)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-ca3e8df872da6346f3e7e751fad30ae4" marker="F643"><p><ref eId="cx38r3zq3-00006" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2002/1792/schedule/V/paragraph/20A/2/k">Sch. V para. 20A(2)(k)</ref> inserted (15.7.2020) by <ref eId="cx38r3zq3-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2020/618">The Social Security (Income and Capital) (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2020 (S.I. 2020/618)</ref>, <ref eId="cx38r3zq3-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2020/618/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="cx38r3zq3-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2020/618/regulation/4/4/c/ii/bb">4(4)(c)(ii)(bb)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-d365bfd9084ee82dd2f708608b7b083a" marker="F644"><p>Words in Sch. V para. 20A(4) revoked (1.4.2013) by <ref eId="cmu8hqya3-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/458">The Council Tax Benefit Abolition (Consequential Provision) Regulations 2013 (S.I. 2013/458)</ref>, <ref eId="cmu8hqya3-00008" class