/2011/2425">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) (No. 3) Regulations 2011 (S.I. 2011/2425)</ref>, <ref eId="cmj07l263-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2011/2425/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="cmj07l263-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2011/2425/regulation/15/7">15(7)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-553e4c11b6d0123efc3ed681652e1877" marker="F651"><p>Words in Sch. V Pt. I para. 23C omitted (1.4.2014) by virtue of <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513">The Social Care (Self-directed Support) (Scotland) Act 2013 (Consequential Modifications and Savings) Order 2014 (S.I. 2014/513)</ref>, <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513/article/1/2">art. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513/schedule/paragraph/7/a">Sch. para. 7(a)</ref> (with <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00010" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513/article/3">art. 3</ref>)</p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-9f5f8b892c6ccefe0324d05496e630ca" marker="F652"><p>Words in Sch. V Pt. I para. 23C(a) inserted (1.4.2014) by <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00017" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513">The Social Care (Self-directed Support) (Scotland) Act 2013 (Consequential Modifications and Savings) Order 2014 (S.I. 2014/513)</ref>, <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00018" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513/article/1/2">art. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00019" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513/schedule/paragraph/7/b">Sch. para. 7(b)</ref> (with <ref eId="cq3dc6dm3-00020" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/513/article/3">art. 3</ref>)</p>